Scenario	             Input Values 	                              Expected Output
Pet eats as expected 	Feeding Time, bin full, weight drops 	        Log “Food eaten”
Pet does not eat    	Feeding time, bin full, no weight drops 	    Alert “Pet did not eat”
Food bin empty 	      Feeding time, bin empty	                      Alert “Refill food bin”
Servo Fails	          Feeding time, bin empty, no change in weight	Alert “Servo failed”
Early Check	          Not feeding time	                            No Action

Suggested Improvements: 
•	Add retry mechanism for servo.
•	Add camera for visual confirmation.
•	Add mobile app integration.
•	Add backup battery for power outage resilience.
